OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe odd spot
OL,6,Fof rain possible in the north at
OL,7,Ffirst, otherwise dry with largely
OL,8,Fclear skies. The odd shower possible
OL,9,Fin the west around dawn. Slight frost
OL,10,Fpossible in sheltered glens.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FMainly dry with some
OL,13,Fbrightness, the odd shower Western
OL,14,FIsles at first. Rain will spread to
OL,15,Fthe west coast late afternoon, then
OL,16,Fspread east in evening. Warm in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
