OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry, bright on Wednesday, then rain in
OL,7,Fthe evening. Cooler with sunny
OL,8,Fintervals and showers on Thursday.
OL,9,FTurning wet and windy on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
